snaps back into the range. 

152
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:36,320
This gets worse with indicators. Moving 
averages bunch up during consolidation.  

153
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:43,600
When price breaks out, the averages cross over. 
This gives retail traders even more confidence. 

154
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:50,160
But smart money set this up. They know exactly 
