designed to separate you from your money. 

159
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:18,880
During consolidations, the difference between 
professional and retail entries is evident.  

160
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:25,280
It's completely backwards from what you'd expect.
Retail traders buy strength. They see price  

161
00:15:25,280 --> 00:15:31,920
