You're providing liquidity. 

175
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:48,720
Think about triangle patterns. You've traded 
these before. Price squeezes into a tight range.  

176
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:55,840
Then breaks out. So you follow the breakout.
But how many times did that work? How many times  

177
00:16:55,840 --> 00:17:03,040
