triangles. Love breakouts. Love momentum. 

179
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:15,280
So they create fake triangles. 
Fake breakouts. Fake momentum. 

180
00:17:15,280 --> 00:17:22,320
You see continuation. They see reversal. 
You see opportunity. They see liquidity. 

181
00:17:22,320 --> 00:17:28,880
The key is thinking like them. Not like retail.
Ask yourself: "If I were managing billions  

182
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:33,600
